abstract: Driven column review of 2016 Audi Q3.
lead_paragraph: The refreshed crossover is easy to park, surgical through urban traffic and easier on fuel than large S.U.V.s, but it is a bit expensive.

headline.main: Video Review: Audi Q3, a Costly Crossover With Few Compromises
headline.print_headline: Audi Q3, a Costly Crossover With Few Compromises
